<p class="nhsuk-body-l">Most messaging service suppliers will not let you choose the channel for a batch message to multiple patients.</p>
<p class="nhsuk-body-l">Avoid sending the same message using more than one channel at the same time. This can overwhelm patients. It also increases costs for the NHS.</p>
